dct_title_s: Map of the Lower Mohican River Basin showing availability of underground water
dct_alternative_sm: Ohio water plan inventory. Underground water resources. Lower Mohican River Basin
dct_description_sm: Text includes information about generalized stratigraphic sequence of the rocks in the Lower Mohican River Basin and quality of underground water.
Scale bar lower left corner of map.
Map side also contains legend and explanation of map symbols.
"Prepared by HENRY L. PREE, JR., Geologist, Ohio Division of Water"
